</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="stops-prop">
<db:title>stops : list&lt;ColorGradientStop&gt;</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the gradient stops describing the gradient.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, this property contains an empty list.</db:para>
<db:para>To set the gradient stops, define them as children of the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtdatavisualization-colorgradient.xml">ColorGradient</db:link>.</db:para>
</db:section>
